      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests must be demonstrated for all governing equations relevant to hemolysis transport at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing was performed only for the momentum equations; hemolysis transport scalar equation was not verified. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
