      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent must demonstrate discretization error below 2% on hemolysis index QoI across all operating points at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence study performed on 3 meshes; Richardson extrapolation yields 8–12% discretization error on hemolysis index — well above the 2% threshold. Achieved level 3 against required level 5."
