      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation must be the same absolute hemolysis index values required for the regulatory submission decision.",
      "rationale": "Validation QoIs include normalized hemolysis index; absolute clinical threshold comparison requires un-normalized values. Partial alignment only. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
