      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be performed on the same pump geometry and at operating conditions spanning the full clinical envelope of the VAD COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump geometry; target device geometry differs in impeller blade angle and gap clearance. Operating conditions cover only 3 of 5 COU flow-speed combinations. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
